org.apache.felix.ipojo.manipulator.util

Class Classpath

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.felix.ipojo.manipulator.util.Classpath
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<String>

    public class Classpath
extends Object
implements Iterable<String>
    An ordered list of classpath elements with set behaviour. A Classpath is immutable and thread safe. This class let retrieve an isolated classloader to load classes from a set of jars.
